BEGIN_PGML
This Venn Diagram groups animals by certain characteristics.

>> [@image(insertGraph($image_1), width=>300)@]*  <<

Name an animal that belongs in the center region. Spelling counts!

[_]{$platypus}{30}

END_PGML

